                        <condition key="deficient">The binding is badly damaged (the front cover is
                           missing, the back board is broken and repaired by means of metal wire and
                           strings). 
 The Ms. is affected by humidity, especially in the upper
                           margin of the folios. 
 Starting from <locus target="#59">59</locus>,
                           parts of the text adjacent to the spine is unreadable.
 The last two
                           folios (<locus from="75rv" to="76rv">75rv-76rv</locus>) are damaged by
                           rodents. 
 <locus target="#1rv">1rv</locus> (blank) is cut (19 x
                           22).
 Cuts skilfully repaired by stitching in <locus target="#3rv">3rv</locus>; 4r; 19rv; 20v; 21r; 28rv; 32v; 33r; 35r; 38r; 40v;
                           74v.
 Crude recent repair by treads in fol. 4.</condition>
