               <history>
                  <origin>
                     <origPlace>
                        <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0163BQM">Māryām Māy ʾAbʾa</placeName>
                     </origPlace>
                     <origDate notBefore="1650" notAfter="1750">Second half of the 17th - first half
                        of the 18th century (?)</origDate>
                  </origin>
                  <provenance>The names of the donors mentioned in the supplication formula, were
                     corrected several (at least three) times.
 The name of a person who was
                     perhaps the original donor, Takla Giyorgis, alongside with his wife’s name
                     Walatta Māryām, has been deleted (washed out) or corrected respectively into
                     Gabra Giyorgis and Walatta Giyorgis (in black ink). Some other names written in
                     the original hand, are still readable: Gabra Krǝstos (<locus target="#3va">3va</locus>, 20ra, 38vb).</provenance>
               </history>
